    {
        "content": "<p>if you care about an elab:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">elab</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"delete_h1\"</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tactic</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">withMainContext</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">some</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ldecl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getLCtx</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">findFromUserName?</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">throwTacticEx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`delete_h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getMainGoal</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m!</span><span class=\"s2\">\"h1 doesn't exist\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">goal'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getMainGoal</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">clear</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ldecl</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">fvarId</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">replaceMainGoal</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">goal'</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
